    "name": "伊松佐河",
    "steam_appid": 1556790,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/221c390439fc468a461cc5c1c47e58fd.poster.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/221c390439fc468a461cc5c1c47e58fd.webm?t=1770380091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/221c390439fc468a461cc5c1c47e58fd.mp4?t=1770380091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/a1deb1cd32ffd75bc0ff2acab4b63709.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">一战战火已经燃到了意大利前线的山区 – 这里风景如画，但也同样残酷致命。参与第一次世界大战中的关键进攻行动，从伊松佐河的第六次战役到惩罚远征，带领你的队伍在意大利北部风景如画的景色和山峰中取得胜利。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《Isonzo/伊松佐河》是由 BlackMill Games 制作的一款逼真战术多人第一人称射击，该公司以其备受好评的真实第一次世界大战战争游戏《Verdun/凡尔登战役》和《Tannenberg/坦能堡》而闻名。沉浸在忠实重现的历史战役中，进行激烈的 48 人对战，考验你的战术技能以及对阿尔卑斯山地战的掌握。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/0b98038b25d5b10f7be832c4dcecf0ba.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/aaf5a7befebf4c598338dc9a53cadcfd.poster.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=175 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/aaf5a7befebf4c598338dc9a53cadcfd.webm?t=1770380091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">决定你的胜利之路：无论你是用手榴弹领导进攻，还是利用山间小道包抄敌人阵地，选择权在你手上。你可以投入战斗，也可以充当辅助角色，切割铁丝网，操纵重机枪和迫击炮。通过独特的信号枪系统，你可以标记目标来进行炮击或让双翼飞机低空飞越，然后再使用刺刀或堑壕棒冲锋，近距离终结敌人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ee65c997e52a33ba20c770f53d3429e2.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/6647cefbe3e0de369f268eb3b0ee09c6.poster.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=175 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/6647cefbe3e0de369f268eb3b0ee09c6.webm?t=1770380091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在六个不同的兵种中进行选择，并从 50 多款标志性一战武器，以及符合史实的装备和各兵种特有的能力中进行选择来打造你的专属配备。你可以扮演狙击手从远处射击敌兵，扮演突击兵横扫敌人防线，或者扮演指挥官下达战术指令，等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/104e587e0919db9ed7e43bc7bf718d36.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=123 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">选好兵种后，挑选各种各样适合人物的制服、配饰和头盔，打造出你专属的兵种。作为点睛之笔，更有几种著名的战时风格胡须可供选择！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/e54a67f56a3fa9e7271559d54274a6f7.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/8220776ff21173e199036b47a53d704b.poster.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=175 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/8220776ff21173e199036b47a53d704b.webm?t=1770380091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从山坡要塞到山地战壕和城市街道，在各种基于历史战役的阿尔卑斯山景观中战斗。了解地形来保持隐蔽并给予敌人出其不意的一击 – 或者更进一步，通过布置沙袋、铁丝网和弹药箱来打造一个动态的战场。战壕潜望镜和狙击盾牌提供了更多的战术选择，但要小心毒气攻击和炮击！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/db6c393730adf2d86425a7836dc398be.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/60798fc8744a0e71d2573ae5805b5309.poster.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=175 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/60798fc8744a0e71d2573ae5805b5309.webm?t=1770380091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《Isonzo/伊松佐河》从第一次世界大战期间为控制阿尔卑斯山而进行的长达数年的战争汲取灵感，向所有玩家呈现了战斗的真实性。从音效、武器和制服，到玩家争夺的房屋、葡萄园和战壕，游戏中的一切均根据研究和实地考察再现。选择你的阵营，并沉浸在历史之中吧！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/8ed857dcf6c50b6a10a194352b6cda5c.avif?t=1770380091\" width=616 height=638 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/4ef11a998fee07898cc4539a2d91dc82.avif?t=1770380091\" width=628 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在《WW1》系列游戏的其他独立作品《Gallipoli/加里波利》Tannenberg/坦能堡》和《Verdun/凡尔登战役》中参与更多的第一次世界大战行动。在凡尔登的西方前线体验战壕战斗，或者在东方前线进行机动，寻求关键战区的控制权。从战争中的各种部队中选择，争夺瞬息万变的前线的控制权。</p>",
